snippet.title: Mindy Minx
snippet.description:
Hi I'm Mindy! I enjoy vlogging daily life. My husband Larry & I are in an age gap marriage with a 30 year age difference. We are just two people who fell in love and we're here to share our story and our future baby journey with others♥️  Wr have two adorable kitties, Lexi & Luna❤️
I also enjoy sharing Day In The Life Vlogs, fashion, beauty, holidays, Harry Potter, & Disney! Spreading love and positivity one video at a time. We hope you join us in this wild and loving journey. XOXO

PO BOX:
Mindy Minx, PO BOX 5927, Hudson, Florida 34674-5927, United States
